    <div class="grid">

      <section>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="intro-box">
              <p><strong>Quick answer:</strong> This blog archive brings together all CRS score guides, Express Entry score tips, cutoff history articles, and Canada PR planning resources in one place. Start with the article that matches your current problem — low CRS score, cutoff confusion, spouse points, language points, education points, or age-based score drop.</p>
