            <div style="margin-top:20px" id="all-posts">
              <div class="section-label">Latest CRS score guides, tips, and Express Entry articles</div>

              <div class="blog-grid">

                <article class="post-card">
                  <div class="post-top">
                    <span class="post-tag">Score Improvement</span>
                    <span class="post-read">18 min read</span>
                  </div>
                  <h2>How to Improve CRS Score 2026 – 10 Proven Ways to Boost Canada Express Entry Points</h2>
                  <p>Learn the fastest and highest-impact ways to improve your CRS score in 2026. Covers IELTS/CELPIP retakes, French bonus, PNP nomination, Canadian work experience, education upgrades, spouse points, and profile fixes.</p>
                  <div class="post-meta">
                    <span class="mini-pill">Language</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">PNP +600</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">CRS boost</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="post-actions">
                    <a class="btn-red" href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/blog/improve-crs-score-tips">Read Guide →</a>
                    <a class="btn-light" href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/">Try CRS Calculator</a>
                  </div>
                </article>

                <article class="post-card">
                  <div class="post-top">
                    <span class="post-tag">Minimum Score</span>
                    <span class="post-read">14 min read</span>
                  </div>
                  <h2>Minimum CRS Score for Canada PR – What You Need to Know</h2>
                  <p>Understand the real minimum CRS score needed for Canada PR through Express Entry. Includes general draw ranges, category-based draw cutoffs, French, trades, healthcare, STEM, and PNP strategy.</p>
                  <div class="post-meta">
                    <span class="mini-pill">Minimum CRS</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">PR chances</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">2026 cutoffs</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="post-actions">
                    <a class="btn-red" href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/blog/minimum-crs-score">Read Guide →</a>
                    <a class="btn-light" href="https://crsscorecalculator.vercel.app/crs-cutoff-scores">View Cutoffs</a>
                  </div>
                </article>

                <article class="post-card">
                  <div class="post-top">
                    <span class="post-tag">Draw History</span>
                    <span class="post-read">12 min read</span>
                  </div>
                  <h2>Express Entry Cutoff History 2015–2026 – CRS Score Trends by Draw</h2>
                  <p>Track how CRS cutoff scores changed from 2015 to 2026. Useful for understanding trend direction, draw volatility, category-based invitations, and realistic future score targets.</p>
                  <div class="post-meta">
                    <span class="mini-pill">CRS trend</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">Draw history</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">Score analysis</span>
                  </div>
