                <article class="post-card">
                  <div class="post-top">
                    <span class="post-tag">Language Points</span>
                    <span class="post-read">11 min read</span>
                  </div>
                  <h2>CRS Score Language Test Guide – IELTS, CELPIP, TEF & TCF Points</h2>
                  <p>See how language scores affect your CRS points. Covers IELTS to CLB, CELPIP, TEF Canada, TCF Canada, CLB 7, CLB 9, language transferability, and French bonus opportunities.</p>
                  <div class="post-meta">
                    <span class="mini-pill">IELTS</span>
