                <article class="post-card">
                  <div class="post-top">
                    <span class="post-tag">Education Points</span>
                    <span class="post-read">10 min read</span>
                  </div>
                  <h2>CRS Score Education Points Guide – Degrees, Diplomas, ECA & Canada Study Bonus</h2>
                  <p>Understand how education affects CRS score. Covers one-year diploma, bachelor’s, two or more certificates, master’s, PhD, ECA requirements, and Canadian study bonus points.</p>
                  <div class="post-meta">
                    <span class="mini-pill">ECA</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">Degree points</span>
