                  <div class="post-top">
                    <span class="post-tag">Spouse Factors</span>
                    <span class="post-read">9 min read</span>
                  </div>
                  <h2>CRS Score with Spouse – How Marriage Changes Canada Express Entry Points</h2>
                  <p>Find out how spouse factors affect your CRS score. Covers spouse language points, education points, Canadian work experience, principal applicant choice, and when applying single may score higher.</p>
                  <div class="post-meta">
                    <span class="mini-pill">Marriage</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">Spouse points</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">PR strategy</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="post-actions">
