                <article class="post-card">
                  <div class="post-top">
                    <span class="post-tag">Age Points</span>
                    <span class="post-read">8 min read</span>
                  </div>
                  <h2>CRS Score by Age – How Age Affects Your Express Entry Points</h2>
                  <p>See the full CRS age points breakdown for single and married applicants. Understand when points peak, how fast they drop after 29, and what to do if age lowers your score.</p>
                  <div class="post-meta">
                    <span class="mini-pill">Age factor</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">Single vs spouse</span>
                    <span class="mini-pill">Point drop</span>
